  SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later

  Kwilt — System Settings → Window Management → KWin Scripts → Configure.

  Plasma 6 KWin scripts use Qt Designer XML (.ui) for their config form, NOT
  QML, despite the rest of Plasma being QtQuick-first. KCM bridges the .ui
  to the kcfg schema in contents/config/main.xml via the widget naming
  convention: every widget named `kcfg_<KeyName>` auto-binds to the kcfg
  entry of the same name. Save in the dialog writes kwinrc; main.js reads
  the same values via cfg() at the next reload.

  Discovery requires metadata.json to declare:
    "X-KDE-ConfigModule": "kwin/effects/configs/kcm_kwin4_genericscripted"
-->
